snippet.title: Rocket Theater: Balance Event Trailer
snippet.description:
Rocket Theater needs your help!
Two new characters have been introduced, as well as a new map.  This event is titled the "Balance Event" because it's time to see how all the current characters compare in creating the best combos they can.

Rocket Theater Rehearsal, a demo containing all the content shown in this video, is now available for download on itch.io!

https://aloe-vertex.itch.io/rocket-theater-rehearsal

Enjoy the Balance Update!
